  <brief_title>Health Economic Assessment of Tygacil® in the Treatment of Secondary Peritonitis in Intensive Care Units (ICUs)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Health Economic Assessment of Tygacil® in the Treatment of Secondary Peritonitis in Intensive Care Units</official_title>
  <sponsors>
