  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main goals of the study are: Assessment of Tygacil's cost-effectiveness; Process cost
      analysis from a hospital perspective (including length of stay, treatment costs, side effect
      management costs, costs of monitoring, costs of diagnostic procedures, cost of care (TISS 10
      score etc.); Efficacy of Tygacil under usual care conditions (cure rate).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
